==Wikipedia dump==
wwwww is a [[Wikipedia:Japan|Japanese]] way of [[Wikipedia:expressing laughter in text-only communication]], deriving from the verb warai (to laugh). It can also be written at the end of a mathematical proof, standing for "Which Was What We Wanted" or "Which Was What Was Wanted". See also: [[Wikipedia:kekeke]], [[Wikipedia:lol]], [[Wikipedia:Q.E.D.]]